name: Electorrent
description: An Electron/Node/AngularJS remote client app for uTorrent server

packageJSON.name: electorrent
packageJSON.description: An Electron/Node/AngularJS remote client app for uTorrent server

releases.name: 2.0.0-beta.2
releases.body:
* Fixed rTorrent ETA, seeds & peers column
* Fixed ratio filter parsing bug
* New animation when changing server
* New save settings animation
* New improved service connection mechanism

releases.name: 2.0.0-beta.1
releases.body:
* Fixed sorting of queue column / resolves #41
* ETA column fix and sorting / resolves #42
* Fixed qBittorrent status queued not showing correctly
* Fixed ratio to only showing 2 decimal places
* Fixed do not show zero as a value for queue
* Fixed seeds and peers for qBittorrent
* Fix ETA no more than one month
* Updated layout settings

releases.name: 2.0.0-beta.0
releases.body:
* More columns, ETA, seed, peers, ratio, queue ect.
* Dynamic and arrangeable columns
* Multiple connection profiles
* Windows file associations in registry
* Updated settings page design

**New:**
- Saving and restoring window size and position

**New:**
- Electron v1.4.10
- Semantic UI v2.2.6

**Bugfixes:**
- Improved support for uTorrent 2.2.1 #27
- Fixed infinite scroll / performance improvement

**New:**
- rTorrent support
- Transmission support (thank you @Paaff)
- Native desktop notifications
- HTTP support for torrent links
- Disconnection notice and popup
- Special thanks to @valdotdev

**Bugfixes**
- Fix adding labels in qBittorrent resolves #16 
- Fix updating settings in qBittorrent resolves #8 
- Thank you valdotdev for reporting

**New**
- All filter for displaying all torrents

**Extensive update - updated GUI, useablity & more!**
- Filter torrents by label as requested in #6 
- Sort torrents by columns as requested in #7 
- Upload _.torrent_ files (Cmd/Ctrl+O) as requested in #9 
- Drag-and-drop support for _.torrent_ files
- Paste torrent magnet links from clipboard (Cmd/Ctrl+I) as requested in #9

- Bug #4 resolved (again)
- Special thanks to kenetik and valdotdev

- Should resolve #4 
- Loading spinner during connecting
- qBittorrent connection improvements

- Now supports qBittorrent!
- Biggest update to Electorrent yet!
- Modular rewrite - supports multiple clients
- New dropdown animation

- Updated to Electron 1.3.3
- Automatic updates for macOS & linux
- Logging for debugging
- Startup command line arguments
- Torrent download speed
- GUI cleanup

- Added support for linux/debian
- Added about page
- Updated to Electron 1.3.2
- Updated dependencies to newer versions

releases.name: v1.0.0
releases.body:
- First release for windows & macOS
- Magnet links for windows/mac
- WebUI API integration
- Electron 1.2.6 framework
